duties_responsibilities.duty: Complete a variety of activities that support the Transportation Department in achieving goals and objectives.
Manage dispatch operations and transportation planning to ensure efficient movement of goods.
Coordinate with suppliers, carriers, and internal teams to optimize inventory management and logistics processes.
Provide excellent customer service and address any transportation-related issues or concerns.
Collaborate with team members to streamline warehouse and transportation operations.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or equivalent (Associate's degree in Logistics or related field preferred)
